text: Embrace the tranquil allure of water and island views from this captivating abode! Situated on a spacious corner lot, this home boasts Pergo laminate flooring, complemented by a custom kitchen featuring maple cabinets & granite countertops. Feel the warmth of the living room, complete with a remote-controlled gas fireplace adorned with faux marble tile surround. Recent upgrades include a 30-year roof & window & doors replacements. Enjoy privacy & ambiance with custom top-down/bottom-up blinds. Outdoors, the cedar fence encloses a double gate, perfect for RV parking on the RV pad, equipped with a 50 amp power connection. Beautiful landscaping accentuated by a newly painted deck & railings. Welcome home to luxury & functionality intertwined!

Welcome to this spacious four bedroom, two full bath home on a large fenced lot. Open Kitchen offers all new appliances, and garbage disposal, with dining room, den/office, and large living room providing open living. Vaulted ceilings in living room, lighten up this oversized room. Master bathroom has a full bath and walk-in closet and additional 3 good sized bedrooms. Two car garage offers lots of storage including loft style storage. Lots of space in the fenced back yard with patio. Home is conveniently close to shopping, schools and I5 for convenient commuting.

Looking for a weekend getaway? Nestled up at the end of the lane, surrounded by Cedar Trees, this private, peaceful 1 bed cabin Camper provides a perfect blend of rustic charm, along w/abundance of outdoor recreational activities such as Tennis, volleyball, horseshoe. Water enthusiasts can enjoy Kayaking, fishing, swimming or hot-tubbing! Prefer quiet? Curl up in a chair, grab a book and your favorite beverage, get cozy listening to sound of a crackling fire on a cozy cool evening.

Nestled within the serene & sought-after Twin Brooks 55+ community, this beautiful single level home is a testament to elegant living amidst landscaped beauty. This lovely home boasts an open & airy floor plan, designed with comfort & accessibility in mind. Each room is bathed in natural light, highlighting the exquisite details and craftsmanship that define the interior. The living room, with its cozy gas fireplace and custom shelving, offers a warm invitation to relax & unwind. The modern kitchen features top-of-the-line appliances, ample counter space w/island & timeless cabinetry that provides plenty of storage while the adjacent dining area is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee while gazing out at the tranquil backyard.

Cozy & Unique custom-built home in beautiful Anacortes! Top quality throughout w/ bamboo & tile floors, granite countertops, Mahogony custom trim, unique windows, gas fireplace, radiant heat & tankless hot water. Kitchen has eating bar, nook for table, walk-in pantry & SS appliances. Guest bedroom, full bath & laundry room on main. Upper floor has huge primary bedroom, gorgeous bath with tile doorless shower, soaking tub and large vanity with storage. Separate room off primary can be used for office, exercise or nursery. This room has French doors out to a covered deck. 24x24 detached garage w/power, water, heat & bathroom. Beautiful covered front porch! So many wonderful features, & close to quaint downtown & ferry! You must see this gem!

Immerse yourself in the serene beauty of waterfront property, boasting a double-sided dock framing majestic vistas of Mt. Baker, the Cascades, & the iconic Rainbow Bridge, all visible from your waterfront home. Entertain guests on the expansive patio, offering the perfect backdrop for every occasion. Inside, relish in the luxury of Italian marble-adorned kitchen, and an inviting island for gathering. Feel the warmth of radiant heat flooring throughout, even extending to the spacious two-car garage. Every corner of this remarkable abode offers panoramic views, promising a lifestyle of unparalleled serenity in addition to the Shelter Bay amenities.

First time on the market! This stunning rambler style duplex is well maintained and ready for new owners. Great investment for owner occupied buyer, investor or multigenerational living. Total sqr ft is 2876. Side A: 3 bdrms & 1.75 baths in 1516 sqr ft. Open floor plan, lrg kitchen w/oak cabinets, eating bar & dining area. 2 car tandem garage with W/D. Side B: 2 large bdrms plus an office, 1.75 baths in 1360 Sqr ft. Unit B upgrades: AC, laminate vinyl plank flooring, granite ctps, newer applcs. Open floor concept w/ dining area, eating bar and gas fireplace. Oversized 1 car garage. Large carport cover, RV parking w/ hook ups, circular drive, covered back deck & shop/shed. Convenient location to the YMCA, shopping, medical and all amenities.

Imagine owning a luxurious custom-built home that offers breathtaking views of the Bellingham Channel and Ship Harbor, serving as your gateway to the enchanting San Juan Islands. This three-level masterpiece is designed with your comfort in mind, featuring an elevator for easy access. On the main floor, you'll discover a versatile studio with a convenient kitchenette and a separate entrance, perfect for guests or a home office. As you ascend to the upper level, the primary suite awaits, boasting panoramic views, vaulted ceiling, a spacious walk-in closet, double vanities & a luxurious walk-in shower. High end features include, granite & quartz countertops, Thermador appliances & Timbertek composite decking to name a few. A stunning home!

The large living room, warmed by an efficient natural gas stove sets the stage for cozy evenings and relaxed gatherings. Hardwood floors grace the sunny dining room of this 3 bedroom, 1.75 bath home. The spacious primary suite is made more attractive by the addition of a sunroom offering additional square footage (approx. 250 sq. ft.) and year-round usability. Outside the easy-care yard and patio provide a pleasant backdrop for outdoor leisure. The roomy attached garage (351 sq. feet) offers additional storage and convenience. Residents of this community enjoy gated privacy along with access to a clubhouse and pool, adding to the lifestyle benefits of owning this home. 55+ Little Mountain Estates. Bonus: storage building for lawn equipment.

Gorgeous, recently remodeled 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home minutes away from Downtown Burlington! This home features an open-concept living space with a large kitchen, dining room and living room that flow seamlessly together. Living room features a cozy fireplace to enjoy in the winter and charming french doors where you can enjoy your private deck & backyard in the summer. Top floor primary suite with a separate deck, walk-in closet and jetted tub! 3 other bedrooms and an additional office space with direct access to the deck. 3 car garage, RV parking and just under half an acre, this property is ready for you to enjoy all of the space it has to offer!

Embark on a journey of opulence in this meticulously crafted residence. Thoughtfully designed floor plan, elegance & comfort abound around every corner; including the vaulted ceiling with beam accents in living rm, primary w/fireplace, luxe ensuite & unparalleled his/her closets. Indulge in the gourmet kitchen featuring quartz, high-end Thermador appliances & walk-in pantry, while in the laundry rm adds practicality & function w/tile dog wash. The 4+car garage w/shop & lower lvl patio offer ample space & room to expand outdoor living. Abundant storage ensures effortless organization. Nestled in a private gated community, relish panoramic vistas of Cascades, Cornet Bay & beyond. Experience luxury living at its finest in this remarkable home.

Low maintenance rambler in a great neighborhood. Great home for downsizing, first home or long-term investment. In great shape and move in ready. Great street appeal and backs up to a quiet greenbelt area. Freshly painted exterior and new roof to be installed Mid-April.

Welcome to your new home in Concrete! This charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom residence boasts 1680 sq ft of spacious living, complete with a dedicated flex space for an office or additional bedroom, you decide. Nestled in a prime location, outdoor enthusiasts will delight in the abundance of nearby activities, from scenic hikes to tranquil fishing spots along the Skagit River. Affordability meets comfort with this property, offering a fenced-in yard perfect for your furry companions to roam freely. Don't miss out on the opportunity to call this inviting haven yours!

This beautifully remodeled home has 4-bed, 2-bath home boasting 1546 sq ft of single-story living. The open-concept kitchen dazzles with extra cabinets, Quartz countertops, a spacious island, walk-in pantry, and stainless steel appliances. Entertain effortlessly on the large patio deck overlooking the expansive, fully fenced backyard complete with a cozy fire pit. Plus, enjoy the convenience of RV parking and additional side parking. Perfectly situated near schools, shopping centers, hospitals, and with easy access to I-5, this home offers both style and convenience in one unbeatable package.

Discover an unparalleled opportunity to own a fee-simple medium bank waterfront retreat boasting breathtaking, uninterrupted views that mesmerize, especially during captivating sunsets. Immerse yourself in the tranquil ambiance of shore living, with the soothing rhythm of waves as your backdrop. Indulge in private beach access on both sides of the residence. Revel in the amenities including tennis court, a boat ramp, clubhouse, and BBQ facilities. This updated two-bedroom, 1.75-bathroom home presents functional yet elegant spaces adorned with beautiful finishes.

Enjoy Country living with this custom 4br 1.75ba partially upgraded home on 4.97 ac that is fenced for horses with round pen and a 3 stall barn with power and water. This 1 1/2 story 1960 sq ft home features a lg living rm with cozy woodstove and slider to patio. Primary bedroom is on ground floor with slider to patio and attached 3/4ba, huge family rm and dining rm with LVP flooring and French doors to backyard, open kitchen w/SS appliances, upstairs there is 3 bedrooms and a full bath and a lg 2 car attached garage, propane heating and private well. Also there is a 36x28 huge shop/barn with carport for plenty of storage and loads of extra parking. This property may qualify for Seller Financing (Vendee). Sold as is.

Amazing fully remodeled gem in town and close to everything! This one checks all the boxes: tons of natural light streaming through the all new windows, brand new appliances, new mini-split heat and A/C, new carpet, tile, and LVP flooring, covered front porch and back deck. Fresh paint both in and out, clean and dry basement cellar, detached garage with 220v and new garage door, garden space, RV parking, and more. Don't miss this fantastic opportunity!

Manufactured home in well kept 55+ park 2bed 2 bath home features new flooring, remodeled master bathroom with soaking tub. Conveniently located to all your needs: shopping, dining, Riverside Health Club, and Coffee Barn to name a few of your potential new favorites. Buyer must to be approved to park.

Cozy, turn of the century home, right in the heart of downtown Burlington. Just a short distance to shopping, restaurants, park and library! Home offers just over 1100sq ft with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 baths. Beautiful renovated kitchen and hall bathroom! original hardwood, newer windows. Fruit trees in backyard and flat area for garden. Super cute shed in backyard with electricity and built in cabinets. RV space with clean out station. This home is completely fenced in backyard!

Discover a breathtaking multi-level home commanding stunning views of Rainbow Bridge, Shelter Bay Marina, and the picturesque golf course. This distinctive property boasts unique features such as grand beams and wood columns, inviting you into a world of architectural marvels. Immerse yourself in natural light streaming through two-story picture windows, illuminating the spacious interior with warmth and charm. Ascend the floating staircase to find a loft primary bedroom, offering unparalleled vistas and a sense of serenity. Welcome to your sanctuary overlooking beauty at every turn. Leased land. Shelter bay offers a marina, golf course, beach access, pool and golf course. Come make this home yours!

This brand new collection of NW contemporary cottage homes built by Strandberg Construction, located at The Crossings, is the perfect balance of spaces designed both for privacy and community. Poised against the lily pad covered pond with walking trails and gathering spaces throughout, invest in the neighborhood garden and future abundance of the orchard. Styled with modern touches, this cottage has two owner suites with elegant baths and an inviting farmhouse kitchen ready for celebration. Clear cedar detailing, solar panels, single car garage and drought resistant landscaping. Built net-zero these cottages enjoy a healthy respect for the incredible natural surroundings and will offer extremely low utility expenses and a 5k+ tax credit.

Immerse yourself in the enchanting embrace of country charm with this captivating 1.5-story farm-style residence! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1.5 baths nestled on 9.8 acres of prime farmland. Every corner of this property exudes warmth and tranquility. Step into the expansive living room with a large window inviting the beauty of the rural landscape into your home with each glance. Indulge your equestrian passions with the barn's 5 horse stalls and a shop. Lush fruit trees and garden plots await your green thumb, promising an oasis of natural abundance. Conveniently located near town amenities, this property offers the perfect balance of rural serenity and urban convenience. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity. Call or book a tour today!

This charming 2 bed, 2 bath rambler boasts a spacious living & dining area filled with natural light. Enjoy your cozy gas fireplace. Beautiful engineered hardwood flooring throughout. Full bath off Primary bedroom. Great size kitchen w/lots of storage and gas range/oven. Adorned w/granite counters, slate floors/backsplash, and SS appliances. Fresh interior & exterior paint. Fully fenced backyard with large covered patio and raised beds for gardening. Enjoy your hot tub and the peace and quiet of this great neighborhood. Bonus room in garage, currently used as a workshop/storage; possible office, 3rd bedroom? Home located close to the medical district, schools, Kiwanis park, shopping, and I-5. Your very own RV parking and guess what? NO HOA!

This brand new collection of NW contemporary cottage homes built by Strandberg Construction, located at The Crossings, is the perfect balance of spaces designed both for privacy and community. Poised against the lily pad covered pond w/walking trails, a community garden & gathering spaces throughout. Styled with modern touches, this cottage has a main level owner's suite w/elegant bath & an inviting farmhouse kitchen ready for your grand celebrations. 2 additional bedrooms and full bath up. Clear cedar detailing, solar panels, single car+ garage and drought resistant landscaping. Built net-zero these cottages enjoy a healthy respect for the incredible natural surroundings & will offer extremely low utility expenses & a 5k+ tax credit.
